<bibRefCitation author="Yokoya" box="[1276,1431,874,899]" pageId="1" pageNumber="128" refString="Yokoya, Y. (1933) On the distribution of decapod crustaceans inhabiting the continental shelf around Japan, chiefly based upon the materials collected by S. S. Soyo-Maru, during the year 1923 - 1930. Journal of the College of Agriculture, 12 (1), 1 - 226." type="journal article" year="1933">
